text: Yar Mohammad Barakzai (born 1923)Yar Mohammed Barakzai's profile at Sports Reference.com was an Afghan footballer and a member of the national football team who competed at the 1948 Summer Olympic Games for his country Afghanistan. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Afghan sportspeople Category:Afghan footballers Category:20th- century Afghan people
